#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:1
msgid "Document Management"
msgstr "문서 관리"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:3
msgid ""
"This chapter covers the four document types, the shared doc mixin, "
"versioning, cross-document references, and tagging."
msgstr ""
"이 장에서는 네 가지 문서 유형, 공유 doc mixin, 버전 관리, 문서 간 참조, "
"태깅을 다룹니다."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:6
msgid "Document Types at a Glance"
msgstr "문서 유형 한눈에 보기"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "Type"
msgstr "유형"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "Model"
msgstr "모델"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "One-per-project?"
msgstr "프로젝트당 하나?"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "Workflow"
msgstr "워크플로우"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "Use Case"
msgstr "활용 사례"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "**CPS**"
msgstr "**CPS**"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "`lu.cxflow.cps`"
msgstr "`lu.cxflow.cps`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "예"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "5-state"
msgstr "5단계"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "Project root — Context / Problem / Solution"
msgstr "프로젝트 루트 — Context / Problem / Solution"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "**CPS Section**"
msgstr "**CPS 섹션**"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "`lu.cxflow.cps.section`"
msgstr "`lu.cxflow.cps.section`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "No (hierarchical)"
msgstr "아니오 (계층적)"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "Nested sections under CPS"
msgstr "CPS 아래 중첩 섹션"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "**Deliverable**"
msgstr "**산출물**"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "`lu.cxflow.deliverable`"
msgstr "`lu.cxflow.deliverable`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "No"
msgstr "아니오"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "5-state + gate"
msgstr "5단계 + 게이트"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "Template-based project documents"
msgstr "템플릿 기반 프로젝트 문서"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "**Report**"
msgstr "**보고서**"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "`lu.cxflow.report`"
msgstr "`lu.cxflow.report`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "2-state"
msgstr "2단계"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "Weekly, gate check, custom reports"
msgstr "주간, 게이트 체크, 커스텀 보고서"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "**Note**"
msgstr "**노트**"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "`lu.cxflow.note`"
msgstr "`lu.cxflow.note`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md
msgid "Meeting, interview, reference, freeform"
msgstr "회의, 인터뷰, 참조, 자유형식"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:16
msgid "CPS — Context / Problem / Solution"
msgstr "CPS — Context / Problem / Solution"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:18
msgid ""
"The CPS is the root document for a project. Each project has exactly one "
"CPS."
msgstr ""
"CPS는 프로젝트의 루트 문서입니다. 각 프로젝트에는 정확히 하나의 CPS가 "
"있습니다."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:20
msgid "CPS Sections"
msgstr "CPS 섹션"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:22
msgid ""
"Sections form a hierarchy with `parent_id` and `parent_path`. Each "
"section has:"
msgstr ""
"섹션은 `parent_id`와 `parent_path`로 계층 구조를 형성합니다. 각 섹션에는 "
"다음이 있습니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:24
msgid "**section_type** — `context`, `problem`, or `solution`"
msgstr "**section_type** — `context`, `problem` 또는 `solution`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:25
msgid "**sequence** — drag to reorder within a parent"
msgstr "**sequence** — 부모 내에서 드래그하여 순서 변경"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:26
msgid "**child_ids** — nested sub-sections"
msgstr "**child_ids** — 중첩된 하위 섹션"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:28
msgid ""
"Sections support recursive serialization to Markdown via "
"`action_serialize_to_md()`, which produces a depth-based heading "
"structure."
msgstr ""
"섹션은 `action_serialize_to_md()`를 통해 Markdown으로 재귀적 직렬화를 "
"지원하며, 깊이 기반 헤딩 구조를 생성합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:31
msgid "Deliverables"
msgstr "산출물"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:33
msgid "Deliverables are template-based documents tied to project gates:"
msgstr "산출물은 프로젝트 게이트에 연결된 템플릿 기반 문서입니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:35
msgid "**template_code** — unique identifier per project (e.g., `PM01`, `AN03`)"
msgstr "**template_code** — 프로젝트별 고유 식별자 (예: `PM01`, `AN03`)"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:36
msgid "**gate_no** — `G1` (Analysis), `G2` (Design), `G3` (Go-Live)"
msgstr "**gate_no** — `G1` (분석), `G2` (설계), `G3` (Go-Live)"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:37
msgid "**auto_level** — controls how templates fill content:"
msgstr "**auto_level** — 템플릿이 콘텐츠를 채우는 방식을 제어합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:38
msgid "`A` — Fully automatic (replace all content)"
msgstr "`A` — 완전 자동 (모든 콘텐츠 교체)"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:39
msgid "`B` — Marker blocks only (selective replacement)"
msgstr "`B` — 마커 블록만 (선택적 교체)"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:40
msgid "`C` — Manual (no auto-fill)"
msgstr "`C` — 수동 (자동 채우기 없음)"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:43
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The engine module (`lu_cxflow_engine`) provides 34 pre-built templates "
"across 8 project phases. See {doc}`engine` for details."
msgstr ""
"엔진 모듈 (`lu_cxflow_engine`)은 8개 프로젝트 단계에 걸쳐 34개 사전 구축 "
"템플릿을 제공합니다. 자세한 내용은 {doc}`engine`을 참조하세요."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:47
msgid "Reports"
msgstr "보고서"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:49
msgid "Reports track project progress with three types:"
msgstr "보고서는 세 가지 유형으로 프로젝트 진행 상황을 추적합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "용도"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "`weekly`"
msgstr "`weekly`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "Weekly status updates"
msgstr "주간 상태 업데이트"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "`gate_check`"
msgstr "`gate_check`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "Gate review results (linked to G1 / G2 / G3)"
msgstr "게이트 리뷰 결과 (G1 / G2 / G3에 연결)"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "`custom`"
msgstr "`custom`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "Free-form reports"
msgstr "자유형식 보고서"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:57
msgid ""
"Reports use a simplified 2-state workflow: **Draft → Approved**. A CxFlow"
" User can directly approve their own reports (the author restriction is "
"relaxed)."
msgstr ""
"보고서는 단순화된 2단계 워크플로우를 사용합니다: **Draft → Approved**. "
"CxFlow User는 자신의 보고서를 직접 승인할 수 있습니다 (작성자 제한이 "
"완화됨)."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:60
#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:79
msgid "Key fields:"
msgstr "주요 필드:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:62
msgid "**period_start** / **period_end** — reporting period"
msgstr "**period_start** / **period_end** — 보고 기간"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:63
msgid "**auto_generated** — flag for system-generated reports"
msgstr "**auto_generated** — 시스템 생성 보고서 플래그"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:65
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "노트"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:67
msgid "Notes capture informal knowledge with four types:"
msgstr "노트는 네 가지 유형으로 비공식 지식을 기록합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "`meeting`"
msgstr "`meeting`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "Meeting minutes with date and participants"
msgstr "날짜와 참석자가 포함된 회의록"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "`interview`"
msgstr "`interview`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "Stakeholder interview records"
msgstr "이해관계자 인터뷰 기록"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "`reference`"
msgstr "`reference`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "External reference material"
msgstr "외부 참조 자료"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "`freeform`"
msgstr "`freeform`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:42
msgid "Anything else"
msgstr "기타"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:76
msgid ""
"Notes use a 2-state workflow: **Draft → Archived**. Both transitions "
"allow the author."
msgstr ""
"노트는 2단계 워크플로우를 사용합니다: **Draft → Archived**. 두 전환 모두 "
"작성자에게 허용됩니다."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:81
msgid "**meeting_date** — date of the event"
msgstr "**meeting_date** — 이벤트 날짜"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:82
msgid "**participant_ids** — linked `res.partner` records"
msgstr "**participant_ids** — 연결된 `res.partner` 레코드"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:83
msgid "**external_url** — link to external resources"
msgstr "**external_url** — 외부 리소스 링크"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:85
msgid "Doc Mixin — Common Features"
msgstr "Doc Mixin — 공통 기능"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:87
msgid "All document types inherit from `lu.cxflow.doc.mixin`, which provides:"
msgstr "모든 문서 유형은 `lu.cxflow.doc.mixin`을 상속하며, 다음을 제공합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:89
msgid "Markdown as SSOT"
msgstr "Markdown을 단일 진실 공급원(SSOT)으로"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:91
msgid ""
"The `md_source` field stores raw Markdown. The `html_cache` field is "
"computed on-the-fly using `markdown-it-py` and sanitized with `bleach`. "
"You never store or edit HTML."
msgstr ""
"`md_source` 필드에 원본 Markdown을 저장합니다. `html_cache` 필드는 "
"`markdown-it-py`를 사용하여 실시간으로 계산되고 `bleach`로 새니타이즈됩니다. "
"HTML을 직접 저장하거나 편집할 필요가 없습니다."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:95
msgid "Slug Generation"
msgstr "슬러그 생성"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:97
msgid ""
"Each document gets a URL-safe `slug` generated from the title after "
"creation. Slugs are unique per model and used for portal URLs."
msgstr ""
"각 문서는 생성 후 제목에서 URL 안전 `slug`가 생성됩니다. 슬러그는 모델별로 "
"고유하며 포탈 URL에 사용됩니다."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:100
msgid "Workflow State Machine"
msgstr "워크플로우 상태 머신"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:102
msgid "The mixin defines a configurable transition policy:"
msgstr "믹스인은 설정 가능한 전환 정책을 정의합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:115
msgid "Reports and Notes override this with simplified 2-state policies."
msgstr "보고서와 노트는 이를 단순화된 2단계 정책으로 재정의합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:118
msgid "Visibility Control"
msgstr "공개 범위 제어"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:120
msgid "Each document has a `visibility` field:"
msgstr "각 문서에는 `visibility` 필드가 있습니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:114
msgid "Value"
msgstr "값"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:114
msgid "Who Can See"
msgstr "조회 가능 대상"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:114
msgid "`internal`"
msgstr "`internal`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:114
msgid "CxFlow Users and Managers only"
msgstr "CxFlow User 및 Manager만"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:114
msgid "`portal_customer`"
msgstr "`portal_customer`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:114
msgid "Internal users + portal customers of the project"
msgstr "내부 사용자 + 프로젝트의 포탈 고객"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:114
msgid "`public`"
msgstr "`public`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:114
msgid "Everyone, including unauthenticated users"
msgstr "인증되지 않은 사용자를 포함한 모든 사람"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:129
msgid ""
"Public documents must be in `approved` state. The system enforces this "
"with a constraint."
msgstr ""
"공개 문서는 반드시 `approved` 상태여야 합니다. 시스템이 제약 조건으로 이를 "
"강제합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:133
msgid "Version Snapshots"
msgstr "버전 스냅샷"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:135
msgid ""
"Every time `md_source` is saved, the version counter increments and a "
"snapshot is created. Each snapshot stores:"
msgstr ""
"`md_source`가 저장될 때마다 버전 카운터가 증가하고 스냅샷이 생성됩니다. "
"각 스냅샷에는 다음이 저장됩니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:138
msgid "**md_source_snapshot** — immutable copy of the content"
msgstr "**md_source_snapshot** — 콘텐츠의 불변 사본"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:139
msgid "**version_number** — sequential counter"
msgstr "**version_number** — 순차 카운터"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:140
msgid "**name** / **state** — document metadata at the time of snapshot"
msgstr "**name** / **state** — 스냅샷 시점의 문서 메타데이터"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:141
msgid "**is_pinned** — pinned versions are never auto-archived"
msgstr "**is_pinned** — 고정된 버전은 자동 보관되지 않음"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:143
msgid "Restoring a Version"
msgstr "버전 복원"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:145
msgid ""
"Click the version count badge → select a version → **Restore**. This "
"writes the snapshot's Markdown back to `md_source` and bumps the version "
"counter (optimistic lock aware)."
msgstr ""
"버전 카운트 배지를 클릭 → 버전 선택 → **Restore**. 스냅샷의 Markdown을 "
"`md_source`에 다시 쓰고 버전 카운터를 증가시킵니다 (낙관적 잠금 인식)."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:149
msgid "Automatic Cleanup"
msgstr "자동 정리"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:151
msgid "A daily cron job archives old versions beyond the configured limit:"
msgstr "일일 크론 작업이 설정된 제한을 초과하는 이전 버전을 보관합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:153
msgid ""
"**Config parameter**: `lu_cxflow_docs.max_versions_per_doc` (default: "
"`50`)"
msgstr ""
"**설정 파라미터**: `lu_cxflow_docs.max_versions_per_doc` (기본값: `50`)"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:154
msgid "Pinned versions are always kept"
msgstr "고정된 버전은 항상 유지됩니다"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:155
msgid "Versions older than 6 months are eligible for deletion"
msgstr "6개월 이상된 버전은 삭제 대상입니다"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:157
msgid "Cross-Document References"
msgstr "문서 간 참조"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:159
msgid ""
"Use the `[[type:id]]` syntax to create inline references between "
"documents:"
msgstr ""
"문서 간 인라인 참조를 생성하려면 `[[type:id]]` 구문을 사용하세요:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:166
msgid "Supported types: `cps`, `cps.section`, `deliverable`, `report`, `note`."
msgstr "지원되는 유형: `cps`, `cps.section`, `deliverable`, `report`, `note`."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:168
msgid "References are tracked in `lu.cxflow.doc.reference` with:"
msgstr "참조는 `lu.cxflow.doc.reference`에서 다음과 함께 추적됩니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:170
msgid "**ref_type** — `inline_link`, `related_doc`, `cited`, `attachment`"
msgstr "**ref_type** — `inline_link`, `related_doc`, `cited`, `attachment`"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:171
msgid "Back-references are computed so each document shows what links to it"
msgstr "역참조가 계산되어 각 문서에 해당 문서를 링크하는 항목이 표시됩니다"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:173
msgid "Tagging"
msgstr "태깅"

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:175
msgid ""
"`lu.cxflow.doc.tag` provides colored tags shared across all document "
"types. Tags are managed under **CxFlow → Configuration → Tags** (CxFlow "
"Manager only)."
msgstr ""
"`lu.cxflow.doc.tag`는 모든 문서 유형에서 공유되는 색상 태그를 제공합니다. "
"태그는 **CxFlow → Configuration → Tags**에서 관리됩니다 (CxFlow Manager "
"전용)."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:178
msgid ""
"Each document type uses its own Many2many relation table for tag "
"assignment."
msgstr ""
"각 문서 유형은 태그 할당을 위해 자체 Many2many 관계 테이블을 사용합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/document-management.md:180
msgid "Menu Structure"
msgstr "메뉴 구조"
